<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But wait! Why=C2=A0<em>sell=C2=A0</em>the bond=
s? Why not=C2=A0<em>borrow=C2=A0</em>against them? You have $100 of bonds, =
$10 of capital kept in cash, $100 of deposits. Rates move against you. In a=
