1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"> down big today</a>, though presumably they=E2=80=99d be down=
=C2=A0<em>more=C2=A0</em>without these measures.) The rescue of Silicon Val=
ley Bank=E2=80=99s depositors comes too late for Silicon Valley Bank=E2=80=
=99s shareholders, but it=E2=80=99s good for every similar bank=E2=80=99s s=
hareholders.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As a matter of rough justice you could imagine=
 the Fed looking at the=C2=A0<em>most=C2=A0</em>similar bank =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0arguably Signature, with its huge proportion of uninsured deposits and i=
ts exposure to fast-money crypto/tech customers =E2=80=94=C2=A0and saying =
=E2=80=9Cno, not you,=C2=A0<em>your=C2=A0</em>shareholders are getting toas=
ted.=E2=80=9D The mechanics of the rescue mean that inevitably some bank sh=
areholders will be bailed out, but not all of them.</p>
