<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But then this weekend <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30821211.285418/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZX=
JnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMTEvY3J5cHRvLXNoYWtlbi1hcy1zdmItZXhwb=
